## Components (Tailwind CSS Utilities + Custom Classes)
**Buttons**
- Primary: Use `bg-teal-500 hover:bg-teal-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium transition-colors`
- Secondary: Use `bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-900 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium transition-colors`
- Outline: Use `border-2 border-teal-500 text-teal-500 hover:bg-teal-500 hover:text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium transition-colors`
- Gradient CTA: Use `bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-emerald-500 hover:from-teal-600 hover:to-emerald-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium transition-all`
- Sizes: `px-4 py-2 text-sm` (small), `px-8 py-4 text-lg` (large)
- Disabled: Use `opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed`
- Full width: `w-full` on mobile, `md:w-auto` on desktop

**Navbar**
- Use Tailwind flexbox utilities: `flex items-center justify-between`
- Sticky: Add `sticky top-0 z-50` classes
- Top bar: Custom dark bar above main navbar (use `bg-slate-900 text-white`)
- Main nav: Use `bg-white shadow-sm` or `bg-slate-50`
- Mobile: Custom hamburger menu button with JavaScript toggle (use `lg:hidden` for mobile button, `hidden lg:flex` for desktop nav)
- Navigation: Use `flex items-center space-x-6` for nav links
- CTA button: Add gradient button inside navbar
- Use classes: `flex`, `items-center`, `justify-between`, `space-x-*`, `hidden`, `lg:flex`

**Breadcrumbs**
- Use Tailwind utilities: `flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-slate-600`
- Custom styling: Use Tailwind typography and spacing utilities

**Service Card**
- Use Tailwind card structure: `bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow p-6`
- Structure: Card container > Image > Card body > Title > Description > CTA button
- Grid: Use Tailwind grid (`grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6`)
- Hover: Use `hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300`
- Use classes: `bg-white`, `rounded-xl`, `shadow-md`, `p-6`, `hover:shadow-xl`, `transition-all`

**Forms**
- Use Tailwind form utilities: `w-full px-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal-500 focus:border-teal-500`
- Form groups: Use `mb-4` or `mb-6` for spacing
- Labels: Use `block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2`
- Validation: Use `border-red-500` for errors, `border-green-500` for success
- Layout: Use `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4` for side-by-side inputs on desktop
- Custom styling: Use Tailwind border-radius and focus utilities
- Use classes: `w-full`, `px-4`, `py-3`, `border`, `rounded-lg`, `focus:ring-2`, `focus:ring-teal-500`

**Feedback**
- Toasts: Create custom toast component with Tailwind utilities (`fixed top-4 right-4 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-4`)
- Modals: Create custom modal with Tailwind (`fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 flex items-center justify-center z-50`)
- Alerts: Use `bg-red-50 border border-red-200 text-red-800 rounded-lg p-4` for error alerts
- Use Tailwind utilities for positioning, colors, and animations

**Loading**
- Use Tailwind spinner: `animate-spin rounded-full h-8 w-8 border-b-2 border-teal-500`
- Skeleton loaders: Use `animate-pulse bg-slate-200 rounded` classes

**Statistics/Metrics Cards**
- Use Tailwind card utilities: `bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center`
- Grid: Use `grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4` (customize for 5 columns on desktop)
- Typography: Use `text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-teal-500` for large numbers
- Use classes: `bg-white`, `rounded-xl`, `shadow-md`, `p-6`, `text-center`

**Tech Capabilities Tags**
- Use Tailwind badge utilities: `px-4 py-2 border-2 border-teal-500 text-teal-500 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-teal-500 hover:text-white transition-colors`
- Responsive: Use `flex flex-wrap gap-2` for wrapping
- Spacing: Use `gap-2` or `gap-3` for consistent spacing
- Use classes: `px-4`, `py-2`, `border-2`, `border-teal-500`, `rounded-full`, `flex`, `flex-wrap`

**Comparison Table**
- Use Tailwind table utilities: `w-full border-collapse`
- Striped rows: Use `even:bg-slate-50`
- Bordered: Use `border border-slate-200`
- Responsive: Wrap in `overflow-x-auto` for mobile scrolling
- Use classes: `w-full`, `border-collapse`, `border`, `even:bg-slate-50`

**Testimonials**
- Use Tailwind card utilities: `bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6`
- Grid: Use `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6`
- Use classes: `bg-white`, `rounded-xl`, `shadow-md`, `p-6`, `blockquote` styling with Tailwind

**Pricing/Packages Cards**
- Use Tailwind card utilities: `bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow p-8`
- Feature lists: Use `<ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">` with list items
- CTA: Use gradient button for "Get Quote" buttons
- Hover: Use `hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300`
- Use classes: `bg-white`, `rounded-xl`, `shadow-md`, `p-8`, `hover:shadow-xl`

**FAQ Accordion**
- Use Tailwind utilities with JavaScript for accordion functionality
- Structure: Accordion container > Accordion item > Button (header) > Collapsible content
- Use `border-b border-slate-200` for item borders
- Use `hidden`/`block` or `max-h-0`/`max-h-screen` with transitions for collapse
- Button: Use `w-full flex items-center justify-between p-4 text-left`
- Content: Use `p-4 text-slate-600` for accordion body

